WEBVTT

01:09.160 --> 01:16.160
The Beauty That You

01:43.560 --> 01:50.560
Are
October 5, 1981

01:52.480 --> 01:59.480
Public Program, Houston, Texas, USA

02:07.180 --> 02:14.180
Yesterday I told you that God has created
us with a purpose and unless and until we

02:22.590 --> 02:29.490
find out our purpose, unless and until we
find out our absolute, we are going to seek

02:29.490 --> 02:36.490
and we are not going to be happy. He has done
everything, very beautifully. Now we should

02:38.430 --> 02:40.620
understand what are we really, inside.

02:40.620 --> 02:47.620
Moreover, as I explained to you yesterday,
that whatever I say is to be taken as a hypothesis,

02:48.959 --> 02:55.720
as a scientist who would keep his mind open
and see for himself, because everything is

02:55.720 --> 03:02.720
not known to you. And whatever I say, you
have to keep your mind open, you need not

03:02.970 --> 03:09.970
accept Me blindly because blind faith is of
no use. But, if you get your enlightenment,

03:12.620 --> 03:19.620
you get your Self-realization, you actualize
it, you become, then you have to verify for

03:20.260 --> 03:24.770
yourself whatever I say, is it true or not?

03:24.770 --> 03:31.770
For example, if I say that the Christ, our
Lord, is placed in this center of ours, at

03:33.760 --> 03:39.700
the Agnya Chakra, which I’ll explain to
you in details. You are not to believe Me

03:39.700 --> 03:46.700
that He’s placed there, but you have to
see for yourself when you get your realization,

03:49.340 --> 03:53.910
you will be able to raise the Kundalini of
other people. And when you start raising the

03:53.910 --> 03:57.570
Kundalini you will find that it will stop
at this point – because you will become

03:57.570 --> 04:04.570
your own gurus, the Kundalini will move at
your fingers, and then when you find the Kundalini

04:05.900 --> 04:12.900
has stopped here you’ll be amazed that you
will have to ask the seeker or the subject

04:14.680 --> 04:21.130
to say the Lord’s Prayer. And that’s the
only way you can get out the Kundalini from

04:21.130 --> 04:28.130
that center. It’s a mantra. It’s a mantra,
it’s a chanting, which was given to us.

04:30.740 --> 04:37.740
He could have given the bija mantra, the seed
of that chanting is Ham-ksham. But, He didn’t

04:38.080 --> 04:44.520
give because He thought people would be, specially
Christians would be very rational people,

04:44.520 --> 04:51.100
so He thought better give a complete explanation
of the whole thing. But every word of it is

04:51.100 --> 04:58.100
a mantra. But it is to be awakened; if it
is not awakened, it’s dead. It is to be

04:58.600 --> 05:01.570
awakened, this is the basis of Sahaj Yoga.

05:01.570 --> 05:06.349
“Saha” is “born.” With you, Saha-ja.
“Ja” means “born” and “Saha” is

05:06.349 --> 05:10.180
“with” – is born with you, spontaneous,
it’s living process within you, is your

05:10.180 --> 05:10.890
own right, you must have it.

05:10.890 --> 05:17.890
So this is a living process and the living
happening should take place. You should become

05:20.240 --> 05:26.220
your absolute; you should become your own
guru; you should get complete integration

05:26.220 --> 05:31.690
within yourself; and then you will be able
to discriminate because the all-pervading

05:31.690 --> 05:38.690
Power, about which I told you yesterday, is
surrounding, is everywhere, only you are to

05:38.840 --> 05:45.840
be awakened; once you are awakened you can
start feeling them, the existence of that,

05:46.060 --> 05:53.060
around you, on your fingers. Imagine on your
fingers you start feeling that Cool Breeze

05:54.850 --> 06:01.850
of the Holy Ghost. That should happen to all
of us and the time has come, the blossom time

06:03.470 --> 06:07.280
has come and thousands must get their realization.

06:07.280 --> 06:13.380
With this today I would explain to you the
different centers we have within ourselves

06:13.380 --> 06:19.270
and the chakras that are within us. I was
amazed, in New York they said that people

06:19.270 --> 06:24.590
are taking lot of money for this chakra therapy,
I mean I just can’t understand what they

06:24.590 --> 06:31.220
do about it, but all those who came from this
chakra therapies, had all their chakras ruined

06:31.220 --> 06:37.360
completely. I mean, you pay to ruin your chakras,
I just couldn’t understand. Anybody coming

06:37.360 --> 06:43.240
from India is not a saint, on the contrary,
as I told you, there could be greatest thuggery

06:43.240 --> 06:50.240
in India. Yes. They are very intelligent,
cunning people, they can be very good. If

06:50.400 --> 06:57.400
they are good, they are very, very good and
if they are bad, they are horrid.

06:57.940 --> 07:04.940
So you have to be careful when you think of
an Indian that, as we cannot say that all

07:06.500 --> 07:13.290
Americans are Mr. Ford, in the same way Indians
also, you must know how to discriminate. First

07:13.290 --> 07:19.150
of all your discrimination power must come,
otherwise you won’t be able to make out

07:19.150 --> 07:26.150
who is the real, who is not the real. That
must happen to you. Unless and until that

07:26.740 --> 07:33.740
happens the rest of it is, is of no use, because
as I said this room is dark and your eyes

07:34.590 --> 07:38.360
are closed, when you come inside you see nothing
but darkness and I start telling you, “this

07:38.360 --> 07:42.620
is this, this is this and I tell you there’s
one elephant you can’t see here and there’s

07:42.620 --> 07:49.250
one tiger sitting here,” you just believe
it. And there’s nothing like that here.

07:49.250 --> 07:55.340
And you people are definitely much more honest
that you can’t believe how people could

07:55.340 --> 07:59.960
be such fake. Oh, there can be fake people
all over the world.

07:59.960 --> 08:06.960
I am ashamed of it sometimes when I see that
in the great country of yoga, where such great

08:10.250 --> 08:17.250
incarnations came in, such great work of the
saints has been done, horrible people also

08:19.020 --> 08:26.020
are born in the same place because that’s
the place they want to harm, they want to

08:27.620 --> 08:34.400
attack. They are negative, not only negative
but they are very, very dangerous. I may tell

08:34.400 --> 08:39.110
about them tomorrow or day after, but today
I want to tell you about the good things that

08:39.110 --> 08:44.229
you are. The beauty that you are and how beautifully
you are made within yourself.

08:44.229 --> 08:51.229
So within us, as I told you, lies this residual
power called as Kundalini. This is the part

08:51.920 --> 08:58.920
of the all-pervading Power which thinks, which
understands, which coordinates, which loves.

08:59.350 --> 09:06.350
Is the integration of all these powers within
us, as this Kundalini. Now so many books have

09:09.449 --> 09:16.300
been written about Kundalini. When I read
them I was shocked that how could people write

09:16.300 --> 09:23.300
books about Kundalini without understanding
what it meant, without understanding where

09:24.880 --> 09:25.130
it was. Such big books have been written on
Kundalini, which says, “The Kundalini is

09:24.880 --> 09:30.690
in the stomach, some say this Kundalini’s
in the nose. I don’t know how could people

09:30.690 --> 09:31.600
write, I mean it takes nothing for them to
write something and to publish, and they are

09:31.600 --> 09:38.600
not afraid of God that they are writing all
these nonsensical things without understanding

09:43.740 --> 09:44.750
it.

09:44.750 --> 09:51.750
So this is the Kundalini that is placed in
the sacrum bone. Now this bone, even in English

09:52.380 --> 09:56.300
is called as sacrum, this word comes from
Greece as I told you that Greek people knew

09:56.300 --> 10:03.300
about Kundalini. Sacrum means sacred. This
bone is a sacred bone. And why is it a sacred

10:04.660 --> 10:11.470
bone because the Kundalini, the primordial
desire within us to be one with the Divine,

10:11.470 --> 10:12.970
is still unmanifested and sleeping, and is
the safest place where it has to be.

10:12.970 --> 10:19.970
Now you are paying attention to Me, now if
I say you pay attention to yourself, you cannot.

10:24.089 --> 10:28.530
You may say, “I’m paying attention,”
but you cannot, you cannot take your attention

10:28.530 --> 10:33.890
inside. But if there is some happening within
you, then your attention is drawn inside,

10:33.890 --> 10:40.890
so it is built like this that at a human level
this happening will take place of sprouting.

10:41.650 --> 10:48.579
And when this sprouting takes place, then
your attention is pulled inside. This attention

10:48.579 --> 10:54.059
has gone out because of the prismatic, as
you say the prism here, prismatic action of

10:54.059 --> 11:01.059
the brain of a human being. I will not go
into the details of it, but there is a big

11:02.670 --> 11:07.199
science about that: why our attention is outside
all the time.

11:07.199 --> 11:14.010
Now below the Kundalini, which is three-and-a-half
coils, is placed a very important center of

11:14.010 --> 11:21.010
innocence, is the center of innocence. The
first thing that was emitted out of the all-pervading

11:21.069 --> 11:27.760
Power was, it had the form, I should say the
all-pervading Power was nothing but just innocence,

11:27.760 --> 11:34.760
which is the most powerful thing in this world,
is your innocence. And this innocence is placed

11:36.610 --> 11:43.610
below the Kundalini, and is adorned by the
deity called as Shri Ganesha, who has a trunk

11:45.089 --> 11:52.089
like an elephant. This is the bija; this is
the seed of Christ. This forms the seed, and

11:52.990 --> 11:58.839
then He incarnated on this earth, this is
the subtle form, on this earth as Mahavishnu

11:58.839 --> 12:05.839
– is written down in the Devi Purana – or
we call Him as Christ. The name Christ and

12:07.809 --> 12:12.870
His name Jesus also has a very big meaning
and relates to something that happened before

12:12.870 --> 12:14.079
Him.

12:14.079 --> 12:21.079
Now this great incarnation of Christ came
on this earth, which was nothing but innocence,

12:22.030 --> 12:29.030
innocence itself took the form and it was
the all-pervading Power itself which took

12:30.079 --> 12:37.079
the form and came on this earth. That’s
why this is a very important center, is the

12:38.510 --> 12:45.510
beginning. Because it is innocence, is like
a lotus and it is placed at a point where

12:45.750 --> 12:52.750
the gate to hell are open within us. This
center gives rise in the gross … Now this

12:54.110 --> 13:01.110
is a subtle center called as Mooladhara Chakra.
Chakra Mooladhara. Mooladhara means the support

13:01.679 --> 13:07.920
of the root. Now root is the Kundalini. It
is the support of the root. Kundalini is the

13:07.920 --> 13:14.370
Mother, and this is your innocence, this is
your childhood and that’s the Mother. And

13:14.370 --> 13:21.370
the Mother is there to give you your realization,
waiting all the time, She is your own individual

13:24.520 --> 13:29.370
Mother, and She is just waiting, ages together,
to give you the experience of Self-realization,

13:29.370 --> 13:32.780
to give you your second birth.

13:32.780 --> 13:39.780
Now the last center looks after, in the gross,
the Pelvic Plexus, which you have heard of,

13:41.319 --> 13:48.319
which has also got four sub-plexuses, this
has also got four petals as we call it. There

13:50.640 --> 13:57.640
are four petals. So this center looks after
the pelvic plexus in the gross, which looks

13:57.860 --> 14:04.860
after the excretion. This center we must consider
at length, a little bit, which is very important

14:06.939 --> 14:13.420
to understand that this also looks after the
sex and reproduction, mainly the sex and other

14:13.420 --> 14:20.420
excretions. Now you can see here that it is
placed below the Kundalini. That means sex

14:23.370 --> 14:30.319
does not play any part in your evolution.
It does not. Those people who say that sex

14:30.319 --> 14:37.319
has something to do with Kundalini, are really
blasphemous and very ugly people because you

14:38.780 --> 14:45.780
cannot put sex to your Mother. It’s something,
even today is not accepted, when people have

14:46.230 --> 14:53.230
become so much lenient about sex, is not accepted.
And this is what it is when people talk of

14:53.569 --> 15:00.510
sex and Kundalini together. As a Mother, I
give them a little chance or sort of a little

15:00.510 --> 15:07.510
grace because to say that they originated
all this from deliberate action will be too

15:08.439 --> 15:13.500
much. I would say that maybe they when they
were meditating, at the sex point they might

15:13.500 --> 15:17.540
have seen Ganesha’s trunk which they might
have thought to be the Kundalini. Possibly

15:17.540 --> 15:23.709
that’s how they went into a wrong situation.
But of course it’s a very wrong thing.

15:23.709 --> 15:30.709
We have had cases in New York and here also
where the private parts of people were touched

15:32.089 --> 15:39.089
by some of the people, and are having a very
bad time with that action. It’s your private.

15:40.130 --> 15:47.130
It has nothing to do with sex. Animals are
more sex-conscious than you are; are they

15:48.870 --> 15:55.329
going to get evolution before you get? Moreover,
the whole thing that is worked out in such

15:55.329 --> 16:02.299
a way that we have started having the sex
through our mental activity, which is a wrong

16:02.299 --> 16:08.520
thing. Christ has said, “Thou shalt not
have adultery, thy should not commit adultery.

16:08.520 --> 16:15.520
But I say, I say verily to you, ‘Thou shalt
not have adulterous eyes.’ Because He knew

16:17.030 --> 16:24.030
this would happen one day that the sex would
move from there to the Swadisthana Chakra

16:24.520 --> 16:31.140
– the second chakra by which we think – and
then it will come into our thinking and our

16:31.140 --> 16:38.140
eyes will start roving around. And then, actually
the sex act minimizes, and it becomes a big

16:40.520 --> 16:45.480
problem; I mean to be a sex point itself becomes
an achievement for people then. It’s such

16:45.480 --> 16:52.480
an absurd thing to do. And this is what is
a very big confusion today in the modern times.

16:52.980 --> 16:59.459
I mean, you cannot make compromises with Christ;
what He said is absolute. But unless and until

16:59.459 --> 17:06.459
you understand that sex as a married life,
as a private thing, is the one that has been

17:09.169 --> 17:16.169
sanctioned for our sustenance, for our sustenance
as human beings; that has to be looked after,

17:19.380 --> 17:26.380
is to be respected, is sacred. And that’s
why anything else that we try to do, all kinds

17:27.380 --> 17:33.890
of perversions and these things – you won’t
believe that all kinds of perversions come

17:33.890 --> 17:38.830
to us because we are no more there. Mostly
we get possessed.

17:38.830 --> 17:45.830
We had one boy who came to us in New York
and he told me, “Mother, I… I’m a man,

17:47.790 --> 17:52.799
I have moustaches and everything but I want
to be like a woman. I want to be dressed up

17:52.799 --> 17:56.410
like a woman,” and he talked like a woman.
He said, “I want to walk like a woman, I

17:56.410 --> 18:01.730
don’t know what to do with myself. I am
so confused. And I cannot have any relationship

18:01.730 --> 18:06.110
with any woman because she gets confused with
me also. And I don’t know what is happening

18:06.110 --> 18:13.110
to me, why I want to be like this.” And
I could see he was possessed by a woman. He

18:13.620 --> 18:20.620
was just possessed by a woman, simple thing
as that. Very simple, it is extremely simple.

18:20.710 --> 18:27.710
And when that possession was removed, he said,
“I am a man again.” Is so simple, in one

18:28.560 --> 18:35.560
day. He is a different man altogether today,
absolutely a different personality, and it

18:36.200 --> 18:38.270
can happen to a woman.

18:38.270 --> 18:44.650
We had somebody from Australia and she got
possessed by a man and she started talking

18:44.650 --> 18:48.260
like that and behavior, the whole thing, her
husband got frightened, and he couldn’t

18:48.260 --> 18:53.780
understand what’s gone wrong with this lady.
And the whole attitude, the whole beauty of

18:53.780 --> 19:00.780
a woman was lost into the style of a man,
and it was so funny and odd to look at. Same

19:01.710 --> 19:08.640
thing: she came to Sahaj Yoga and the spirit
ran away. She is a beautiful woman now, extremely

19:08.640 --> 19:11.430
beautiful, and they’re having a very good
relationship.

19:11.430 --> 19:18.430
So when you try to do anything perverted with
the sex and do not respect it, you do not

19:19.180 --> 19:24.850
know what things are awaiting us around. So
before I go to other chakras, I want to tell

19:24.850 --> 19:31.420
you about our other unknown areas which are
very important to us and then we’ll go to

19:31.420 --> 19:32.960
the second chakra.

19:32.960 --> 19:39.960
As you see here on the left hand side this
blue line is there. This blue line is our

19:40.920 --> 19:47.920
power of desire by which we desire, by which
God has – supposing this is the primordial

19:50.290 --> 19:54.610
being because God has made you in His own
image – supposing it is the image of God,

19:54.610 --> 20:01.610
then it is His desire. This power of desire
gives you existence, and when this desire

20:01.700 --> 20:08.700
is over, when the Spirit, which is watching
the drama of this body, gets fed up, it disappears,

20:11.110 --> 20:18.110
then the death comes in. This power of desire
is the left side. We call it in Sanskrit as

20:20.050 --> 20:27.050
Ida Nadi, also called as the Moon Nadi and
in the Hatha Yoga is the Tha Nadi. This is

20:27.510 --> 20:33.940
the channel, is a subtle channel. But this
gives rise to the gross channel, which is

20:33.940 --> 20:37.950
the left sympathetic nervous system. Now,
doctors don’t believe that left and right

20:37.950 --> 20:42.380
sympathetic nervous systems are two different,
but you will find out yourself that they are

20:42.380 --> 20:49.380
very different. This looks after our emotional
side, and also beyond this lies the area which

20:51.840 --> 20:57.870
is unknown to us, is the subconscious; it
is unknown to us. Whatever is unknown is not

20:57.870 --> 21:04.840
God, is not from God’s area. It is an unknown
area, and beyond that subconscious area, lies

21:04.840 --> 21:11.840
the collective subconscious – all that has
died from our creation. Recently I was seeing

21:14.330 --> 21:21.330
one of the series on cancer, in London on
the television, and they told that they have

21:24.240 --> 21:31.240
discovered some sort of proteins, which they
call as protein 58 and 56 and all that, they

21:31.630 --> 21:38.630
have given names, which they have also photographed
– enter into our being from areas which

21:43.180 --> 21:48.630
are built within us, from unknown areas – they
do not know if they are known areas – which

21:48.630 --> 21:53.350
are built within us since our creation. Now,
I’ve told this about ten years back in America

21:53.350 --> 21:58.160
before. And they trigger the happening of
cancer, they trigger it.

21:58.160 --> 22:05.160
So it is from the collective subconscious
this attack comes in. So if you move to the

22:07.410 --> 22:13.870
left side, you move to the collective subconscious
too much and then all kinds of things can

22:13.870 --> 22:20.870
happen to you. For example, first of all you
start getting shaking, you start hearing voices,

22:21.380 --> 22:27.020
you start feeling that you are losing your
body; you are going on top of some place and

22:27.020 --> 22:33.870
seeing things. Is all these spirits are doing.
Now it has reached such a serious state, that

22:33.870 --> 22:40.870
in Switzerland I found that many children
were killed because of this action. The mother

22:42.910 --> 22:48.740
is, supposing, with some clairvoyant lady
or somebody who is doing this spiritual work.

22:48.740 --> 22:53.480
Is a very dangerous thing. One should never
take to this kind of a thing. If you take

22:53.480 --> 22:59.400
to these things, then seven generations suffer.
Today only I had a girl who told Me that her

22:59.400 --> 23:04.110
mother was a clairvoyant, and all her life
she was miserable with her husband and this

23:04.110 --> 23:09.180
girl has been always crying and weeping and
she cannot conceive or something like that.

23:09.180 --> 23:13.680
Is a very serious thing, one should never
go into these unknown areas of the collective

23:13.680 --> 23:19.790
subconscious and worry about the dead and
control them and look after them and call

23:19.790 --> 23:26.790
them. You must give them their freedom. Is
a very dangerous area into which you enter.

23:27.190 --> 23:31.200
I hope you don’t mind it, I have to tell
you the truth, I am your Mother, and I have

23:31.200 --> 23:35.870
to tell you the truth: that you should be
very careful about this kind of thing like

23:35.870 --> 23:41.840
psychics or the people who try to say that
“You can get possessed.” They will not

23:41.840 --> 23:45.730
say, they say, “It is, it is–” They
can even say, “This is Holy Ghost.” They

23:45.730 --> 23:52.460
can say anything. But in whatever way, when
you find that you are not in control of the

23:52.460 --> 23:58.810
situation, that means you are not there. Is
very simple as that, supposing your car is

23:58.810 --> 24:05.440
driving and suddenly it goes into a khadd
[pit – ED.]. Now, do you think that you

24:05.440 --> 24:11.440
have achieved a greater progress by that?
It’s just you have moved without your control.

24:11.440 --> 24:16.799
If you have no control upon yourself …If
somebody sitting down and he starts jumping

24:16.799 --> 24:23.799
– automatically, he cannot control his jumping
– then it is not himself, minimum of minimum.

24:23.990 --> 24:30.990
Whatever he is, even that control is lost.
Anything, any such happening which is beyond

24:31.960 --> 24:37.430
your control means that you are enslaved by
one of these possessions. But they are never

24:37.430 --> 24:39.660
satisfied with what they do to you.

24:39.660 --> 24:45.620
I mean like I’ll tell you one of the very
startling example of this left side. In London

24:45.620 --> 24:52.350
we have – I don’t know now if they have
but we had – a center called, “Late Dr.

24:52.350 --> 24:58.270
Laing’s International Curative Center.”
I didn’t know about it, but a lady came

24:58.270 --> 25:01.530
to Me in India to tell Me about this.

25:01.530 --> 25:08.170
She said she had some problem with her stomach
and she wrote to this organization saying

25:08.170 --> 25:12.310
that “Please, help me to get cured.”

25:12.310 --> 25:16.470
And they wrote back saying that “At five
o’clock on such-and-such date, we’ll enter

25:16.470 --> 25:22.000
into your body.” I mean they were honest,
I must say, as English people are honest sometimes.

25:22.000 --> 25:26.400
So he was honest to say that “We’ll enter
into your body, some of the doctors are there

25:26.400 --> 25:31.760
who will enter into your body, and they’ll
cure you.” But afterwards, after five years

25:31.760 --> 25:37.570
the lady was rattling, rattling just like
a junkie car. And she came to Me and then

25:37.570 --> 25:41.950
she gave Me the history of this, which I verified.

25:41.950 --> 25:47.270
The Dr. Laing, the Dr. Laing, the one, the
one who is the one who is supposed to be running,

25:47.270 --> 25:54.270
is late, he’s dead. He entered into a soldier
in Vietnam, an American, and told him that

25:57.330 --> 26:01.090
“You go and talk to my son and tell him
that I have entered into you and that you

26:01.090 --> 26:06.840
should start such and such organization.”
Now this soldier has never done anything,

26:06.840 --> 26:12.420
I mean he has never seen a scalpel also, he
doesn’t know how to operate, no question.

26:12.420 --> 26:18.460
