27:07.470 --> 27:12.490
Now the people who think too much about their
past, “What was my previous life?” Why

27:12.490 --> 27:18.190
should you worry? Whatever it was is better
today because you can get realization today.

27:18.190 --> 27:23.620
You could not get realization even if you
were the King of Egypt, what does it matter?

27:23.620 --> 27:29.360
You couldn’t get your realization that day,
so why worry about the past? All the time

27:29.360 --> 27:33.740
worrying about the past or playing with your
emotions, you see. Like we had one gentleman,

27:33.740 --> 27:40.320
who used to always cry and weep too much and
his mother sent him to Me, and I asked him,

27:40.320 --> 27:41.330
“What did you do all your life?”

27:41.330 --> 27:44.870
He said, “I was very fond of Lord Byron
and I just read him.”

27:44.870 --> 27:50.590
I said, “All right, that’s it.” This
Lord Byron, he led such a horrible life himself,

27:50.590 --> 27:53.190
an unholy person, and made everybody cry,

27:53.190 --> 27:55.530
“You suffer, you must suffer, you must weep.”
