28:11.250 --> 28:17.270
that you showed Him as a resurrection, that
is His message. Is resurrection is His message.

28:17.270 --> 28:24.270
Crucifixion is just a means but resurrection
is the thing. And the lanky-panky stuff, walking

28:25.740 --> 28:32.450
like a saint, how can that be? Is it possible,
a person who is bestowed with God’s blessing

28:32.450 --> 28:38.860
has to be a healthy, cheerful and a very happy
person, has to be that. Minimum of minimum

28:38.860 --> 28:45.370
should be that, and I was happy to see even
Mr. Paulsen here, who was very healthy and

28:45.370 --> 28:51.200
this thing I said, “Now, this is a religious
place because wherever I go I find such serious

28:51.200 --> 28:51.820
and absolutely sickly people.”

