people. They have not accepted Me. They didn’t

29:31.820 --> 29:35.480
accept Christ, and because they didn’t accept
they couldn’t accept that He suffered for

29:35.480 --> 29:41.510
us. Why should we suffer? Has He suffered
less for you any way: has He left some for

29:41.510 --> 29:48.140
you to suffer? So, you want to suffer, all
