30:16.410 --> 30:22.240
in ‘82 in any case we are going to be finished,
waiting for– they discussing it very nicely.

30:22.240 --> 30:28.290
Les Miserables I call them, as they are. So
why should you suffer, I just can’t understand,

30:28.290 --> 30:35.290
when Christ has suffered for you? Only He’s
to be awakened within us. If He’s awakened,

30:35.320 --> 30:41.480
He takes away all our sufferings, all our
conditionings, all our so-called karmas and

30:41.480 --> 30:46.090
everything, which I will show you later on
how it works out.

30:46.090 --> 30:50.880
So now we come to the left side then to the
right side. Right side is the action, the

30:50.880 --> 30:57.880
power of action, is the Surya Nadi, is the
channel of the sun. When you want to enact

31:00.770 --> 31:07.770
your desire, manifest it, then you use this
action power, Iccha Shakti is called in Sanskrit.

31:08.940 --> 31:14.470
Now this power works mainly through this second
center, or we call it the third center, actually

31:14.470 --> 31:20.750
it is the third because the second one is
that. This center is called as Swadisthana

31:20.750 --> 31:27.750
and this center has got six, you can see six
plexuses, it’s like the Star of David.

31:29.820 --> 31:36.820
Moses preached something, and Jews are doing
something else. Christ preached something,

31:40.480 --> 31:45.570
and Christians are doing something else. Adi
Shankaracharya taught something, and Hindus

31:45.570 --> 31:49.990
are doing just the opposite. Mohammed taught
something, and they did just the opposite.

31:49.990 --> 31:55.630
It’s not only in religion, in every way
you see how we are perverted. Like this center

31:55.630 --> 32:02.630
is used for converting the fat in your stomach
for the use of your brain. Nor do we realize

32:06.660 --> 32:12.920
that our brain is made of fat. Do we know
all our nerves are made of fat. Now there’s

32:12.920 --> 32:19.760
a general principle in this country that you
should not use any butter, which is very wrong.

32:19.760 --> 32:25.640
When you don’t use any butter how are you
going to supply this brain with something,

32:25.640 --> 32:29.200
I mean where will you get, it’s completely
drained out.

32:29.200 --> 32:36.200
You use your brain so much, so much so, that
this poor center has to work only for your

32:37.100 --> 32:42.270
thinking which has no productivity. You just
go on thinking, thinking, thinking, thinking;

32:42.270 --> 32:46.850
two horns come out of your head of thinking;
still you are thinking, and they go on growing,

32:46.850 --> 32:52.300
you cannot stop your thinking. And what are
you thinking, what have you got out of your

32:52.300 --> 32:53.070
thinking?

32:53.070 --> 33:00.070
This right side is the one which is our five
elements also, five elements within us. So

33:02.750 --> 33:09.750
when we started discovering what is the essence
of the five elements, in India we started

33:11.679 --> 33:17.010
the Vedas thousands of years back, and the
effect of that is shown now, is the science,

33:17.010 --> 33:23.380
you discovered, the science. That you understood
how to master these five elements. But what

33:23.380 --> 33:28.580
did you do with it? You created bombs; horrible
bombs you have created. You have created these

33:28.580 --> 33:35.000
devils and now you are frightened of them.
Thank God. That’s something good that all

33:35.000 --> 33:40.429
such ventures stop by themselves because you
create a bomb, it becomes a devil on top of

33:40.429 --> 33:45.900
your head. Now you can’t start war because
as soon as you start means no more existence.

33:45.900 --> 33:50.090
So you are frightened and that is how – where
have we gone to?

33:50.090 --> 33:56.429
Science has led us to which sensible things,
we should think. For example science has given

33:56.429 --> 34:03.320
us all these devices by which our life can
be made very easy. We can have more time,

34:03.320 --> 34:10.230
we can have much more time than our forefathers
had, who had to do everything with their own

34:10.230 --> 34:14.809
hands and go about it, but here, you see,
everything is instant. I mean anything: You

34:14.809 --> 34:19.780
want to have food? All right you have instant,
everything is made instant. But for what is

34:19.780 --> 34:25.770
it instant, is to save time. Now we have watches
also here to save time, everybody’s saving

34:25.770 --> 34:31.270
time, saving time, everybody “busy” saving
time. But what are you doing about the saved

34:31.270 --> 34:36.399
time? What do we do with it? For example there
was a gentleman coming from India, very busy

34:36.399 --> 34:40.059
man, “Very busy, there’s no time to talk
to anyone.”

34:40.059 --> 34:46.159
And I said, “Wanna, why are you in such
a great hurry to go?”

34:46.159 --> 34:48.819
“Oh, you don’t know! I have very important
–“

34:48.819 --> 34:49.069
“What?”

34:48.819 --> 34:51.639
“I have to attend a particular ball for
five hours there.”

34:51.639 --> 34:54.359
“Very good. Is that the way you are going
to save?”

34:54.359 --> 34:59.950
“And then I have to attend a racecourse,
I have to do this, I have to do that.” This

34:59.950 --> 35:05.760
is no saving of time; this is the real waste
of time. Real waste of time is this way we

35:05.760 --> 35:12.760
do it, and how are we going to save our time?
Time is to be saved to be realized, to be

35:12.829 --> 35:18.759
in meditation, to enjoy the beauties of God.
That’s why these all things are given to

35:18.759 --> 35:23.450
us, and that’s how we should look at them.
But now we have become their slaves.

35:23.450 --> 35:30.450
When we achieve something, for example electricity,
it is so important to New York that one day

35:30.519 --> 35:36.460
it stopped, the whole thing stopped. So we
become also slaves to these. Apart from that,

35:36.460 --> 35:42.759
now we have no time, we are so busy. I don’t
know. I thought that here people will have

35:42.759 --> 35:46.989
more time than we have in India because, you
see, if you have to travel we have very funny

35:46.989 --> 35:52.279
trains, and we have not yet developed as you
people are. Sometimes I have to go to villages

35:52.279 --> 35:57.579
in bullock carts and this and this. But people
have no time. This is the trouble in these

35:57.579 --> 36:03.059
countries, you have no time at all and I don’t
know what constructive work they are doing

36:03.059 --> 36:03.720
for themselves.

36:03.720 --> 36:10.109
So this is what is the right side where we
go wrong. But the worst thing we do is to

36:10.109 --> 36:17.109
think. We think all the time, and what do
we think? Either we think of aggression or

36:19.670 --> 36:26.670
we think of recession. For example we think
that, “Oh, we are guilty.” You do something

36:27.559 --> 36:31.450
and then you sit down, “Oh, I should not
have done it, this is very wrong I should

36:31.450 --> 36:38.019
not have done it,” and you start wondering
about it, correcting about it. But actual

36:38.019 --> 36:44.079
correction is not there, actual correction
is not there, only by thinking you avoid the

36:44.079 --> 36:49.749
main issue. You have to be in the present
but thinking can only take you to the left

36:49.749 --> 36:55.119
or to the right, to the past or to the present.
[future – ED?] You cannot be at the state

36:55.119 --> 37:00.749
where you become just yourself, there’s
no thought. There is no mental activity at

37:00.749 --> 37:07.450
all, you just become. Because a thought rises
like this and falls off, another thought rises

37:07.450 --> 37:12.579
like that and falls off, in between them is
a very little space which is the present.

37:12.579 --> 37:18.440
So the past comes to the future and becomes,
again the future comes in and again becomes

37:18.440 --> 37:24.999
the past like that. But in between is the
present and that present is very small.

37:24.999 --> 37:30.980
Unless and until you know how to stay in that
present, you will be always tossing on these

37:30.980 --> 37:37.980
waves of past and future while past is finished
and future doesn’t exist. You plan out something,

37:38.150 --> 37:44.309
it – all plans goes out. You plan anything
but how can you plan also, I can’t understand.

37:44.309 --> 37:49.579
Supposing you don’t know the way, and you
plan that, “I will go right and left.”

37:49.579 --> 37:52.069
Now supposing you are going to the right and
left is the sea, will you jump in the sea?

37:52.069 --> 37:59.069
Anything that you have to do new, you cannot
plan it out, you have to keep it just open,

38:00.619 --> 38:07.619
like a seed when it sprouts, it has got a
living cell at its tip. It goes and sees for

38:07.970 --> 38:14.049
itself how it has to move. When there is hardness,
it moves round the hardness, when there is

38:14.049 --> 38:15.339
softness, it moves like that.

38:15.339 --> 38:21.559
So when we plan everything we really become
rigid, and like – I heard of a person who

38:21.559 --> 38:26.420
planned everything for his picnic. He had
all champagne and everything put together

38:26.420 --> 38:31.910
and when he reached the place he had no bottle
opener and he had to break the bottles. That’s

38:31.910 --> 38:37.339
what it is. Sometimes the planning can be
such a headache, I mean, you waste one hour

38:37.339 --> 38:42.579
in planning and while it comes to reality
you find it’s all wrong, it doesn’t work

38:42.579 --> 38:48.109
out. So too much planning, like I have to
go supposing to Los Angeles, I have to book

38:48.109 --> 38:51.989
My ticket, this is today, I have to do it
today. I don’t have to sit down and plan

38:51.989 --> 38:54.450
that on such and such date I’ll go and book
it.

38:54.450 --> 38:58.549
So in the present if you know how to live,
but this cannot be done by saying that “You

38:58.549 --> 39:02.970
live in present.” It cannot be done, I know
because that’s not some sort of a thing

39:02.970 --> 39:08.069
that can be taught. It has to happen to you,
you have to become that. Once you become that,

39:08.069 --> 39:15.069
then you become thoughtlessly aware. You become
a witness. You see the whole show as a drama,

39:15.970 --> 39:20.589
and you don’t get involved into it. You
just see the waves coming up and going down.

39:20.589 --> 39:26.900
Like, I can say, you are standing in the water,
and there are waves around and you are frightened,

39:26.900 --> 39:33.739
but if you are put in the boat you start seeing
those things. If you know how to swim you

39:33.739 --> 39:33.989
can enjoy those waves.

39:33.819 --> 39:39.880
In the same way when you become a master,
when you come in the boat in the state of

39:39.880 --> 39:43.390
thoughtless awareness then you start seeing
these things and the whole thing appears like

39:43.390 --> 39:48.779
a drama. Actually the whole thing is a drama
but the drama must end for you to see that

39:48.779 --> 39:54.559
it’s just a drama and you are unnecessarily
worried about it, and by worry, you know for

39:54.559 --> 39:58.589
definite nothing works out. But if I say,
“Don’t worry,” you’ll worry more,

39:58.589 --> 40:04.079
that’s not the way. That’s not the way.
They all tried these tricks to say, “Don’t

40:04.079 --> 40:07.369
do that and don’t do that,” it never worked.
With human beings it doesn’t work out. It’s

40:07.369 --> 40:11.670
all right with animals, you can work it out,
but with human beings, if you tell them, “Don’t,”

40:11.670 --> 40:18.140
they’ll do it ten time. So best is to so
make them that. Unless and until they are

40:18.140 --> 40:23.710
made the spirit it’s impossible to convince
a modern man to do something. So is best is

40:23.710 --> 40:28.940
first let them have their realization, let
them have their light, let them see for themselves

40:28.940 --> 40:33.450
what’s the problem, let them feel it and
correct it. It’s let them judge themselves,

40:33.450 --> 40:40.210
that is the best way is to do it, and that’s
the time has come for you to have it and see

40:40.210 --> 40:47.210
for yourself and be able to discriminate between
false and reality.

40:47.269 --> 40:54.269
Now this side beyond is the supraconscious
area, and beyond this is the collective supraconscious.

40:56.489 --> 41:03.489
Now if you take LSD, for example you take
LSD, you go onto supraconscious area. I was

41:06.400 --> 41:13.400
surprised when I went to Colombia, I asked
them, they had a condor as their emblem for

41:13.619 --> 41:19.559
navy, and I said, “How condor is your emblem?”
because condor has nothing to do with the

41:19.559 --> 41:19.989
navy.

41:19.989 --> 41:26.989
They said, “Our old Indians have told us
that a God called Shri Vishnu,” just see

41:27.049 --> 41:33.160
the name, “came on a condor.” And really
condor is the conveyance of Vishnu. Can you

41:33.160 --> 41:38.910
imagine? I was amazed at this. How did these
people in thousands of years backs saw, but

41:38.910 --> 41:43.220
then I said, “What were they doing normally,
what was their pastime?” And they showed

41:43.220 --> 41:50.220
Me a thing made out of a shell of a fruit
and with a little stirring rod in it.

41:53.789 --> 41:54.799
I said, “What is this?”

41:54.799 --> 41:56.559
They said, “They used to make some sort
of a amrose.”

41:56.559 --> 41:58.329
“Oh, I see, that’s it.”

41:58.329 --> 42:03.869
And even today Peru is exporting that amrose
to you which is nothing but LSD.

42:03.869 --> 42:09.759
If you take things like that, of that nature,
of LSD nature, you go to the right side. You

42:09.759 --> 42:14.400
move to your supraconscious area. Means you
get disintegrated.

42:14.400 --> 42:19.099
In the morning I told you that when you are
integrated you don’t see any auras or anything

42:19.099 --> 42:23.299
around the person. When you are disintegrated,
only then you see because you become these

42:23.299 --> 42:29.170
five elements. When you are integrated you
don’t see anything. And then you start seeing

42:29.170 --> 42:34.229
these things, like an eye and a light, and
all those things you start seeing, and if

42:34.229 --> 42:41.229
you go further, further with it into supraconscious
areas, you can become horribly possessed by

42:42.519 --> 42:49.519
the people who have been ambitious. Even Hitler
can possess you. Hitler did that. Hitler did

42:50.259 --> 42:56.200
all supraconscious activity in Germany. How
he possessed people was through supraconscious.

42:56.200 --> 43:01.200
Because in the supraconscious, collective
supraconscious, there are many ambitious people

43:01.200 --> 43:07.400
who have died. Like Gauguin was an ambitious
man, but he became mad, I don’t know how

43:07.400 --> 43:12.729
he became mad. Normally an ambitious man doesn’t
become mad he makes everyone mad, but he doesn’t

43:12.729 --> 43:17.509
become himself. But this fellow was possessed,
and we saw it in the television that a man

43:17.509 --> 43:22.410
who was possessed by this Gauguin was painting
just like him. I know – you see Gauguin’s

43:22.410 --> 43:27.150
paintings, that you must be knowing also that
in one line he puts lots of color and he was

43:27.150 --> 43:30.779
doing it very fast. And he said, “I’m
possessed by Gauguin.”

43:30.779 --> 43:35.630
So these ambitious people, like some of the
ambitious people could be doctors, could be

43:35.630 --> 43:42.630
mathematicians, can be physicians or anything
like that, they can possess.

43:43.779 --> 43:50.729
I know of a lady, she is a unique mathematician
and she’s possessed, definitely possessed.

43:50.729 --> 43:53.739
And she can tell you anything you ask her,
any square root, anything she can tell you,

43:53.739 --> 43:58.170
and she’s earning lot of money out of it
but she’s always sick, she has a headache.

43:58.170 --> 44:01.410
She came to Me for curing, I said, “You
have to give up this nonsense.”

44:01.410 --> 44:03.979
She said, “Let me make sufficient money,
then I’ll give up.”

44:03.979 --> 44:10.089
I said, “By that time I may not be there.”

44:10.089 --> 44:14.190
So these things can happen to you with the
supraconscious activity and this awareness

44:14.190 --> 44:19.880
of supraconscious is also very dangerous.
The trouble is if you suffer from the superego

44:19.880 --> 44:26.739
there, from this side, with the conditionings,
