Like an eighty-year-old woman writing love
letters to an eighteen-year-old boy. It’s

45:52.079 --> 45:58.009
stupidity. Is absolute stupidity, I tell you,
if you see it from wisdom point of view. One

45:58.009 --> 46:02.650
can’t understand an old man, who is like
a great-grandfather, writing a love letter

46:02.650 --> 46:07.930
to a little girl of eighteen years or an old
woman, who could be a great-great-great-grandmother

46:07.930 --> 46:11.210
writing to a little boy like that, it’s
absurd. And they are so stupid and they talk

46:11.210 --> 46:17.729
like this, “I believe in this.” Of course
