46:37.930 --> 46:41.799
seeing it when you get your realization.

46:41.799 --> 46:48.799
I had a disciple, one of My sons, who came
to Me and one day he said, “Mother, I’m

46:51.049 --> 46:51.970
really frightened with one idea.”

46:51.970 --> 46:53.259
I Said, “What is it?”

46:53.259 --> 46:55.559
“But You don’t tell me if it is true.”

46:55.559 --> 46:56.829
I said, “What is it?”

46:56.829 --> 46:59.130
He said, “Was I Napoleon in my last life?”

46:59.130 --> 47:01.170
I said, “What makes you think like that?”

47:01.170 --> 47:05.609
“Because I can see such a big ego on my
head, this could be only Napoleon and I know

47:05.609 --> 47:10.279
how to draw. These two things put together,
could I have been Napoleon, but if I was You

47:10.279 --> 47:14.630
don’t tell me otherwise I may commit suicide”
– even after realization.

47:14.630 --> 47:21.630
So it is ego becomes then a headache to us.
It becomes a headache and we want to get rid

47:21.950 --> 47:27.559
of it. We start seeing it, and it presses
you, you get a headache and you feel it in

47:27.559 --> 47:34.009
the Agnya, how it troubles you. Then it starts
troubling you – not others so much as it

47:34.009 --> 47:36.999
troubles you – because you don’t want
to accept that you are egoistical, you start

47:36.999 --> 47:41.319
seeing it. But you don’t say that you have
a ego, you will come and tell Me, “Mother

47:41.319 --> 47:45.119
I’ve got an Agnya catching,” and we have
to clear that Agnya. Nobody feels bad about

47:45.119 --> 47:50.809
it because you are separated from yourself.
You don’t feel that you are hurt or insulted

47:50.809 --> 47:55.380
because you get separated, and you see for
yourself. Like this sari has some sort of

47:55.380 --> 47:59.910
a black spot on it, so I see it, I take it
out, and then I want to wash it, I don’t

47:59.910 --> 48:02.239
want to keep it black; I am not identified
with it.

48:02.239 --> 48:07.640
So all these fixations also drop out when
you get realized, because you go in the center,

48:07.640 --> 48:09.410
not on the left or to the right.

48:09.410 --> 48:16.410
Now movement on the right, actually is the
blessing of this center, in the center, because

48:19.940 --> 48:26.940
the central line is this line of our evolution,
is the line of sustenance, is the line by

48:27.319 --> 48:29.690
which we have become human beings.

48:29.690 --> 48:36.690
First of all we get our sustenance, like we
can say the gold is untarnishable. That is

48:37.829 --> 48:44.279
the sustenance of gold. We can say carbon
has four valences, in the same way human beings

48:44.279 --> 48:50.910
have ten valences – they are in the stomach.
These are the ten sustenance described as

48:50.910 --> 48:57.910
the Ten Commandments in the Bible. They all
can be explained very well in Sahaj Yoga.

48:58.029 --> 49:05.029
This is the human sustenance which is around
in that part which we call as Void. It’s

49:06.099 --> 49:13.099
not the same Void, or is the gap, as the Zen,
but this is the Void, we mean the space where

49:14.619 --> 49:21.619
we exist in our evolutionary state. Now this
center is the one that is presided over – this

49:24.170 --> 49:30.920
one, the second one is presided over by the
Creator, and this one is through the Preserver,

49:30.920 --> 49:31.609
the one who preserves.

49:31.609 --> 49:37.859
Now there can be a problem with people who
believe that there is one God. I also believe

49:37.859 --> 49:42.779
the same thing. I mean, it is true: He – there’s
only one God, but He has different aspects.

49:42.779 --> 49:49.430
God doesn’t exist like, say, Rock of Gibraltar.
Even Rock of Gibraltar, if you see, it has

49:49.430 --> 49:56.430
got aspects. God has aspects like a gentleman,
now say for example if a gentleman is a minister

49:56.499 --> 50:01.950
here, he could be a husband, he could be a
father, he could be a brother, he could be

50:01.950 --> 50:07.499
anything. So God has different aspects and
out of that the first aspect, as I told you

50:07.499 --> 50:13.809
of the existence, the power of existence,
that does not incarnate on this earth, it

50:13.809 --> 50:19.450
does not incarnate, it just exist, it watches,
it sees, and that is in the heart, which is

50:19.450 --> 50:26.450
the Spirit – expression of that God Almighty
who is watching the spectacle of His Power.

50:29.349 --> 50:35.200
Now the other aspect of God is that He’s
a Creator, He creates all these galaxies and

50:35.200 --> 50:42.200
all these things now as I told you yesterday
about the Vishuddhi Chakra, we are this center

50:43.660 --> 50:50.660
which is America, that if this center is awakened
here, you don’t have to have any missiles

50:51.999 --> 50:58.809
or anything. As in the Saturn, you have got
a girdle around, you too have that girdle

50:58.809 --> 51:04.739
around America and nobody can touch you, but
you are to be awakened first of all. If you

51:04.739 --> 51:11.739
are awakened in that center, nobody can touch
you. Russia is going to know about it, they

51:14.690 --> 51:18.279
have to know about it because they are getting
into parapsychology and all these things and

51:18.279 --> 51:22.809
they are going to get possessed about this.
They have to know through their supraconscious

51:22.809 --> 51:25.279
that you are the people who are awakened.

51:25.279 --> 51:30.609
Once you are awakened nobody can touch you,
because there’s a girdle round you, and

51:30.609 --> 51:36.279
there are sixteen sub-plexuses as there are
sixteen, you have seen there are sixteen substar

51:36.279 --> 51:38.009
– sub, what do you call them?

51:38.009 --> 51:38.690
Warren: Moons

51:38.690 --> 51:45.690
Shri Mataji: Moons, they call them moons,
sixteen moons around Saturn. And you are one

51:46.950 --> 51:52.839
guided by Saturn. Saturn makes this country.
Saturn has made this country, and this is

51:52.839 --> 51:57.529
the Vishuddhi Chakra which is a very important
chakra about which I’ll tell later.

51:57.529 --> 52:04.529
So this center we come to of our evolution.
Is presided by the Preserver, the aspect of

52:05.019 --> 52:12.019
preservation, He’s the Father who looks
after us; He’s the One who gives us our

52:12.799 --> 52:17.880
wellbeing. He comes on this earth again and
again in different forms. According to Indian

52:17.880 --> 52:24.880
Puranas, the Ark of Noah was saved by a fish,
which was a dolphin, and this dolphin fish

52:27.390 --> 52:34.390
was this aspect which incarnated. Then the
second aspect came as the tortoise, then the

52:36.099 --> 52:42.839
third as a quadiped. Like that they have described
the evolution, how these incarnations had

52:42.839 --> 52:49.839
to come to break the barriers of the evolutionary
ignorance. These are the people who came for

52:52.059 --> 52:59.059
the break-through. Ultimately a short man
was created called as Vamana, then a very

52:59.710 --> 53:04.440
fiery, big man, he’s called as Passidon,
[Poseidon – ED] in Greek language.

53:04.440 --> 53:10.979
Greeks made their gods look like human beings;
I mean they never kept their purity. See,

53:10.979 --> 53:15.609
everybody was given with some quality of a
human being. I don’t know why they did it

53:15.609 --> 53:22.039
but that’s how they spoiled the whole game.
Now this god, the god, which we can say or

53:22.039 --> 53:29.039
the incarnation that came on this earth was
a fiery man, a man who fought the nature,

53:31.089 --> 53:38.089
who fought all the different elements. And
then after that came another aspect on this

53:40.890 --> 53:47.890
earth, who was Shri Rama, is the ideal king,
the king who is a benevolent king, the One

53:50.529 --> 53:57.150
who gave us the political idea about how to
govern – Shri Rama – this was eight thousand

53:57.150 --> 53:57.960
years back.

53:57.960 --> 54:04.960
Then came the incarnation, after that the
incarnation came in the center here, before,

54:05.190 --> 54:11.579
before Rama, this incarnation was of the Goddess,
of the primordial Mother. She Herself incarnated

54:11.579 --> 54:18.579
on this earth before Rama, because many forces
which were negative were collected by the

54:18.650 --> 54:25.019
ignorance of human beings, and the seekers
were very much harmed. So She came on this

54:25.019 --> 54:32.019
earth to kill those horrible, demonic forces
and to destroy them and to save the seekers,

54:33.150 --> 54:39.589
Her children, to save them from this drowning
into the sea of illusion, and She came on

54:39.589 --> 54:45.160
this earth. As they say she came thousand
times, but actually She came many-a-times

54:45.160 --> 54:47.119
before Shri Rama came in.

54:47.119 --> 54:53.359
Then came Shri Rama who came on the right-hand
side of the heart. Now this is also a very

54:53.359 --> 54:59.170
important center within us. Those people who
have problems with the fatherhood. Like today

54:59.170 --> 55:04.950
there was a girl who was catching on the right
hand, this heart, this is the center. We asked

55:04.950 --> 55:11.089
her what about her father, and she told Me,
“My father is dead but he’s still guiding

55:11.089 --> 55:11.729
me.”

55:11.729 --> 55:16.499
I said, “That’s not good, you must give
relief to your father. He should be given

55:16.499 --> 55:18.749
freedom, and you will feel better.”

55:18.749 --> 55:25.210
And people with this heart get asthma. This
side, this problem, on this finger we feel,

55:25.210 --> 55:29.999
get asthma, problems with their breathing…
All these things can be cured if you just

55:29.999 --> 55:36.759
tell them that, “You ask your father to
leave you and to be born again and forget

55:36.759 --> 55:43.759
about it.” It works wonders, we have seen.
But recently a doctor in England has performed

55:44.289 --> 55:51.289
some experiments with, what you call, anorexia
– there’s a disease anorexia, where the

55:53.329 --> 55:58.109
girls just don’t eat any food. He found
out that these girls, when they were told

55:58.109 --> 56:03.650
about their father, and that a rite can be,
I mean the after death rites can be done and

56:03.650 --> 56:07.489
all that, they felt all right and they got
rid of it.

56:07.489 --> 56:11.900
Can you imagine this is experimented and found
out now; I mean this we have been doing for

56:11.900 --> 56:16.339
the last ten years, but recently it has been
found out that if a girl is suffering from

56:16.339 --> 56:22.479
this disease of anorexia, you can cure it;
if the father is dead, then only it happens.

56:22.479 --> 56:29.479
So fatherhood –a man who is not a good father,
a man who has a bad father, a girl who is

56:30.359 --> 56:37.359
too much attached to the father or a girl
who is not treated nicely also by her husband

56:38.270 --> 56:42.650
– also the husband is there – if he doesn’t
look after her well, she can suffer.

56:42.650 --> 56:47.119
Now the center part, this one – the one
he’s there [Warren is showing on the Virata

56:47.119 --> 56:51.680
Chakra chart] – center heart, it’s also
a very, very important center where the Goddess

56:51.680 --> 56:58.680
– the world, we say the Mother of the World,
Jagadamba She’s called – has incarnated.

56:59.440 --> 57:06.440
Is a very important thing for us, because
when you suffer, say, from any insecurities,

57:07.089 --> 57:14.089
then this center starts going into palpitations,
this center starts vibrating very much. Till

57:15.519 --> 57:21.650
the boy is of twelve years or a girl is of
twelve years, in the sternum bone the antibodies

57:21.650 --> 57:28.650
are created by this center. This center creates
the antibodies and they circulate in the whole

57:28.660 --> 57:34.839
body and remain there, and whenever there
is an attack, either from a entity or from

57:34.839 --> 57:39.999
any disease or anything, these antibodies
fight it. And that is the center which is

57:39.999 --> 57:45.459
very important, specially for women. If their
motherhood is challenged or if they are insecure,

57:45.459 --> 57:51.180
if their husbands are making them insecure
by any of their behavior, then they develop

57:51.180 --> 57:58.180
this trouble of this center, where they may
get breast cancer. Breast cancer comes to

57:58.589 --> 58:05.589
women when they are insecure. Only it can
be cured when this center is awakened; breast

58:06.190 --> 58:12.660
cancer can be very easily cured, if they could
be secured through awakening of this center

58:12.660 --> 58:15.670
of the Mother of the Universe.

58:15.670 --> 58:21.640
And then we have the center up there, which
is the Vishuddhi Chakra, which is a very important…

58:21.640 --> 58:28.640
for you, because it is adorned by the completion
of this evolution as called as Virat – it

58:34.269 --> 58:41.269
is Shri Krishna, who is the complete incarnation
of this primordial being. And He is placed

58:43.279 --> 58:50.279
there. It is He who is the witness, who is
watching. When the Kundalini rises over this,

58:56.019 --> 58:58.400
you start witnessing the whole thing.

58:58.400 --> 59:04.749
It has got sixteen sub plexuses and which
look after your face, your nose, eyes, ears

59:04.749 --> 59:11.749
and all these places. And when this center
is out, then you have all kinds of problems.

59:13.130 --> 59:20.130
Say the left side, left side Vishuddhi Chakra
catches when you feel guilty, when you are

59:20.299 --> 59:24.549
diffident. When you start thinking that, “It
is very wrong too, I should have not done

59:24.549 --> 59:29.559
this,” and all that, then the left Vishuddhi
catches. Or also with smoking it catches;

59:29.559 --> 59:36.559
smoking spoils this center very much. Imagine
in America the percentage of smokers is the

59:37.049 --> 59:43.369
maximum. Can you imagine, in this center only
where they are born, this is the maximum here?

59:43.369 --> 59:50.369
Like England is the heart of the universe,
where they are lethargic. Europe is the liver

59:50.549 --> 59:57.549
of the world where they are drinking. America
is the Vishuddhi of the world where they are

59:58.400 --> 01:00:02.739
smoking. What a justice done to themselves
and to God, their Creator! So smoking is against

01:00:02.739 --> 01:00:08.660
this center. Thank God now it is established
that it causes cancer, but still people are

01:00:08.660 --> 01:00:12.499
smoking, they say, “What does it matter?”

01:00:12.499 --> 01:00:17.059
But this is a very, very important center
for us because this is the time when we raised

01:00:17.059 --> 01:00:21.559
our head, this center came up. Now see the
ego and superego start developing actually

01:00:21.559 --> 01:00:28.559
from here. So this gives rise to ego and superego.
Somebody is a very arrogant person, catches

01:00:29.989 --> 01:00:35.469
on the right; who is a very aggressive type
he catches on the right Vishuddhi. In the

01:00:35.469 --> 01:00:42.469
center, a person who is against God, who is
anti-God, who is against collectivity, who

01:00:47.880 --> 01:00:54.880
is talking against God, who is openly saying
things against God, catches on this center.

01:00:55.950 --> 01:01:02.529
So this center, as it is, is very important
for you, because if you can awaken this center

01:01:02.529 --> 01:01:07.349
within you here, as I’ve told you, you become
as powerful as Shri Krishna.

01:01:07.349 --> 01:01:14.349
Shri Krishna has a Samhara Shakti. He has
the power to kill; He has four special things

01:01:16.130 --> 01:01:21.680
with Him, four weapons by which He kills,
but one of them is this, in His hand, is a

01:01:21.680 --> 01:01:28.680
discus and this discus is shown around the
Saturn which you see. And with this discus

01:01:29.359 --> 01:01:36.359
at any distance He can destroy. So His destructive
powers are built in you. Nobody can destroy

01:01:38.989 --> 01:01:45.739
you. You have to just get to your Self and
become your Self. You’ll become so powerful

01:01:45.739 --> 01:01:52.739
a nation – but powerful in loving, in being
compassionate and affectionate, in the real

01:01:54.029 --> 01:01:59.959
sense of the word, not the way we are now
trying to help others; is not the way. It

01:01:59.959 --> 01:02:04.660
can be very disgraceful sometimes; the way
we try to help others can be very disgraceful.

01:02:04.660 --> 01:02:10.279
You will be amazed how, sometimes you people
have helped and have created problem for others.

01:02:10.279 --> 01:02:17.279
I’ll give a very simple example which is
really surprising and astonishing. Some years

01:02:18.349 --> 01:02:23.150
back we had a dearth of wheat, and people
sent horrible wheat to India, horrible, that

01:02:23.150 --> 01:02:29.029
even the animals would not eat. Just to help
us, you see. We are not so badly off people;

01:02:29.029 --> 01:02:34.719
we are very fussy about food. We may be poor
but we don’t eat everything; we are very

01:02:34.719 --> 01:02:41.719
fussy. So people threw away that wheat outside.
That wheat grew into a grass, which was called

01:02:41.900 --> 01:02:48.900
as “Congress Grass,” can you imagine,
and that grass started moving from the roads

01:02:49.019 --> 01:02:56.019
to the fields, from the fields to all the
trees and started engulfing them. It was like

01:02:56.119 --> 01:03:03.119
a mad grass, it was like a malignant grass,
eating away everything that there was. Imagine,

01:03:04.170 --> 01:03:09.890
as it is we had dearth of thing and this thing
came, and we didn’t know what to do with

01:03:09.890 --> 01:03:10.469
it.

01:03:10.469 --> 01:03:15.849
So we tried some Sahaj Yoga tricks and it
has worked, and thank God that grass is now

01:03:15.849 --> 01:03:22.469
finished. But from that grass you had sent
some other seeds of acacia, and these also

01:03:22.469 --> 01:03:28.329
people threw away. Out of this came out such
horrible trees of acacia that it has got thorns

01:03:28.329 --> 01:03:32.670
which are poisonous. And in the villages they
have grown so big that children can’t play

01:03:32.670 --> 01:03:38.650
and if they touch that they get very seriously
ill. It’s a very seri– which you have

01:03:38.650 --> 01:03:45.479
done so innocently. There’s no grace about
it, I think, the way it was done, and that’s

01:03:45.479 --> 01:03:49.779
how we can create problem through our help
to others because what is there to help. Who

01:03:49.779 --> 01:03:53.779
is the other?

01:03:53.779 --> 01:03:58.539
If you are the collectivity, if you are Shri
Krishna, then what are you helping? You are

01:03:58.539 --> 01:04:02.969
helping yourself, this is your own finger.
If you help your own finger, you don’t help

01:04:02.969 --> 01:04:09.569
it in a different way than you help other
fingers. That means you become collective

01:04:09.569 --> 01:04:16.569
being, and you are. People like Abraham Lincoln,
as I said yesterday, and great people in this

01:04:16.910 --> 01:04:23.910
country established these great ideals of
liberty. And the liberty, they said that,

01:04:25.059 --> 01:04:32.059
even Roosevelt once said that “Poverty anywhere
is a threat to prosperity anywhere.” What

01:04:33.709 --> 01:04:39.819
at great thing to say, to feel that, that
oneness with others, that anywhere poverty

01:04:39.819 --> 01:04:43.319
is a threat to our prosperity!

01:04:43.319 --> 01:04:48.670
All this collectivity has been expressed by
your great men in this country, not only but

01:04:48.670 --> 01:04:55.670
the sense of responsibility because it is
on your shoulders, the responsibility. Responsibility

01:04:58.069 --> 01:05:05.069
of making others the Self, realize, is your
responsibility. You are the responsible nation,

01:05:07.459 --> 01:05:12.579
you are responsible for the whole universe,
whatever things you do here that goes outside.

01:05:12.579 --> 01:05:17.119
You took to rock ’n roll, people started
doing rock ’n roll, you did anything nonsensical

01:05:17.119 --> 01:05:19.890
that started going abroad. Anything nonsensical
you do here spreads everywhere because Americans

01:05:19.890 --> 01:05:25.660
are doing. Jeans, now everybody wears, even
in India! Imagine in that hot country they

01:05:25.660 --> 01:05:32.660
are wearing very strong, starched ones, and
they get all kinds of problems with that,

01:05:34.130 --> 01:05:37.869
circulation problems [INDISTINCT: I mean?],
but… “Americans are doing,” everybody

01:05:37.869 --> 01:05:39.789
is becoming American in India.

01:05:39.789 --> 01:05:44.670
That’s it, in every developing country you
have put your hand; you have interest in everyone,

01:05:44.670 --> 01:05:51.670
but should be done after realization when
you feel the pangs of others, you feel the

01:05:52.549 --> 01:05:59.549
heart, you feel the real pain of others within
yourself, and you do it, not because you want

01:06:00.469 --> 01:06:03.410
to do it for others, but do it because you
want to save yourself out of that pain. You

01:06:03.410 --> 01:06:10.190
do it for yourself. If somebody’s drowned
and you try to save a person who is drowned,

01:06:10.190 --> 01:06:13.910
then you don’t save him you actually are
saving yourself because something in you is

01:06:13.910 --> 01:06:18.930
getting drowned there. And that happens to
you when you become that collective being,

01:06:18.930 --> 01:06:25.190
when you become the Spirit, then it happens
to you. Before that, whatever you do is disgraceful,

01:06:25.190 --> 01:06:31.459
sometimes can be harmful, can be very ugly
and sometimes it can be so grotesque that

01:06:31.459 --> 01:06:33.989
people say, “All right, you keep your help
to yourself, we don’t want to have any more

01:06:33.989 --> 01:06:40.989
of this.” I mean you take away all the self-respect
of people.

01:06:41.099 --> 01:06:48.099
So one has to understand that you stand here
in this world, in this universe as a collective

01:06:49.809 --> 01:06:54.400
being, as the representative of that collective
being at this Vishuddhi Chakra and you have

01:06:54.400 --> 01:07:01.400
to give with your hands. For giving. This
applies to your hands and you must give, those

01:07:02.089 --> 01:07:07.390
hands which have never given are no good,
they are very insensitive hands, you must

01:07:07.390 --> 01:07:12.660
give, and that must come into you, and not
giving for giving’s sake, but Nirvach,,

01:07:12.660 --> 01:07:19.660
as they say, without any, any return about
it. Nothing, is just giving, just flowing,

01:07:19.989 --> 01:07:25.739
just like the Sun’s rays are coming to you,
they don’t want anything in return, do they?

01:07:25.739 --> 01:07:32.739
Just flowing. When that should happen, if
Sahaj Yoga takes to it, I hope it takes to

01:07:35.039 --> 01:07:40.469
America that Americans accept Sahaj Yog, that
it works out. You have already got all kinds

01:07:40.469 --> 01:07:46.069
of horrible people here. I don’t know how
you are going to work it out, but God willing,

01:07:46.069 --> 01:07:50.219
with your determination, I am sure.

01:07:50.219 --> 01:07:56.640
This is the first Unity Church I’m visiting
and I hope that in other Unity Churches also,

01:07:56.640 --> 01:08:02.839
it will be made convenient for Me and we can
save other people also, and they can become

01:08:02.839 --> 01:08:09.839
realized souls and they can become the Vishuddhi
Chakras, the responsible people, men of God,

01:08:14.759 --> 01:08:19.259
those who have to become prophets, that they
are responsible that they have to make others

01:08:19.259 --> 01:08:26.259
also prophets and save so many seekers who
