01:10:28.920 --> 01:10:35.920
Seeker: Sometimes in meditation and in chanting,
a person will be rocking. Would you consider

01:10:48.580 --> 01:10:52.470
that a negative thing?

01:10:52.470 --> 01:10:58.440
Warren: Sometimes in meditation people will
rock or move. Is this a negative thing?

01:10:58.440 --> 01:11:04.210
Shri Mataji: Absolutely, absolutely. You should
not rock, there should be no movement, the

01:11:04.210 --> 01:11:09.110
eyes should be steady, there should be no
movement in the eyelids, nothing. This rocking

01:11:09.110 --> 01:11:16.110
is absolutely wrong. All these things should
not happen to you, that’s not meditation.

01:11:16.310 --> 01:11:23.210
Meditation is where you are absolutely normal,
you are always in meditation after realization,

01:11:23.210 --> 01:11:25.350
you are in meditation.

01:11:25.350 --> 01:11:31.980
Question: I’ve studied with Paramahansa
Yogananda the SRF, Self-Realization Fellowship,

01:11:31.980 --> 01:11:38.980
and one of the things they teach is to focus
the eyes, with the eyes closed only on the

01:11:40.740 --> 01:11:41.190
[INAUDIBLE].

01:11:41.190 --> 01:11:47.610
Shri Mataji: I must say that I don’t want
to start any controversy. That’s one thing

01:11:47.610 --> 01:11:54.610
sure, but I’ll tell you that proof of the
pudding is in the eating. Let’s go this

01:11:55.870 --> 01:12:00.990
way. First of all logically we should see,
we have to get baptism through here, not through

01:12:00.990 --> 01:12:06.490
here. Do we get baptism through here? If the
door is here what’s the use of breaking

01:12:06.490 --> 01:12:13.490
this window? And focusing and effort is not
going to give you realization, is wrong. You

01:12:17.700 --> 01:12:22.890
see this pampers– human effort, you see
it pampers you that you can put in an effort.

01:12:22.890 --> 01:12:28.170
You cannot. One must accept this position:
we cannot put in an effort for a living thing.

01:12:28.170 --> 01:12:33.830
For example, as I told you, for a seed if
you have to sprout it you have to put it in

01:12:33.830 --> 01:12:38.390
the Mother Earth. You cannot pull it out,
isn’t it? Whatever you may try, you cannot

01:12:38.390 --> 01:12:45.390
pull it out and sprout. You cannot put in
any effort. Any effort is wrong, is against

01:12:48.230 --> 01:12:51.870
spontaneity and living things. So no effort
is needed as such.

01:12:51.870 --> 01:12:58.870
Lady: I’d like to ask Her about that center
where the immune bodies develop, at what age

01:13:01.120 --> 01:13:08.120
and what can we do in order to make that immunity
get bigger or…

01:13:14.800 --> 01:13:21.800
Warren: She says two questions. At what age
does the immune bodies start developing and

01:13:23.000 --> 01:13:27.780
secondly is there any way in which you can
expand the capacity of the immune bodies?

01:13:27.780 --> 01:13:33.200
Shri Mataji: Of course, of course. Of course,
that is what Sahaj Yoga is. When you become

01:13:33.200 --> 01:13:37.750
the truth, all untruth falls off, is that
is what Sahaj Yoga is; absolutely that is

01:13:37.750 --> 01:13:42.230
what it is. Tomorrow, I am going to tell you
about Christ and about cancer; about all these

01:13:42.230 --> 01:13:46.070
immune bodies how we fight them. That may
be day after tomorrow, I don’t know, but

01:13:46.070 --> 01:13:50.280
tomorrow, may not be, but day after tomorrow
I’ll tell you how to grow into it. Absolutely.

01:13:50.280 --> 01:13:57.280
You learn how to protect, you learn how to
fight. Absolutely. That is what happens after

01:13:59.600 --> 01:14:05.830
realization then you must learn the divine
technique, not before realization. After realization,

01:14:05.830 --> 01:14:12.830
not before. Before it is connected what’s
the use of playing with it? It has to be connected

01:14:13.000 --> 01:14:14.040
first.

01:14:14.040 --> 01:14:17.160
What is it?

01:14:17.160 --> 01:14:21.320
Warren: Any other questions?

01:14:21.320 --> 01:14:28.320
Man: What are the avenues available to keep
these channels open?

01:14:31.850 --> 01:14:35.890
Warren: What are the avenues available to
keep the channels open?

01:14:35.890 --> 01:14:42.890
Shri Mataji: To be your Spirit. And we will
let you know later on how to work it out,

01:14:43.310 --> 01:14:49.400
how to balance yourself, how the imbalances
are there. This I’ll do it on Wednesday.

01:14:49.400 --> 01:14:55.760
I will tell you how to keep them clear, how
to keep your chakras clear, how to work it

01:14:55.760 --> 01:14:58.970
out, everything I’ll tell you. And also
–

01:14:58.970 --> 01:15:03.640
[We don’t have a book about it, isn’t
it, but in any case –

01:15:03.640 --> 01:15:04.000
Warren: We’ve got the “Advent.”

01:15:04.000 --> 01:15:04.920
Shri Mataji: Oh yes. ]

01:15:04.920 --> 01:15:11.400
We have a very big book on this Sahaj Yoga,
which of course we do not sell to everyone,

01:15:11.400 --> 01:15:18.400
but we’ll see about it. We’ll see about
it because you people are growing very fast.

01:15:18.830 --> 01:15:23.290
If you people really grow, then we’ll sell
it to you also, but normally we don’t sell

01:15:23.290 --> 01:15:23.920
it to everyone.

01:15:23.920 --> 01:15:28.020
Question: Do you feel Hatha Yoga is necessary?

01:15:28.020 --> 01:15:34.070
Shri Mataji: Not at all, nothing. On the contrary
Hatha Yoga creates a problem, I told you in

01:15:34.070 --> 01:15:39.610
the morning, to a lady who was doing Hatha
Yoga. I told her how Hatha Yoga in the modern

01:15:39.610 --> 01:15:46.610
times means nothing but physical acrobats.
It is not that. Hatha Yoga was practiced about,

01:15:46.670 --> 01:15:52.230
I don’t know how many years back, about
eight thousand years back, when we had a different

01:15:52.230 --> 01:15:59.230
system of life, where children from five to
twenty-five lived with a guru who was a realized

01:15:59.350 --> 01:16:06.350
soul, and led a very celibate life. To such
an extent that, that university, any university

01:16:06.670 --> 01:16:13.670
– say somebody’s university was Vishwamitra,
then that realized soul was Vishwamitra and

01:16:14.110 --> 01:16:18.710
that university people could not marry, even
today they cannot marry. Even today they cannot

01:16:18.710 --> 01:16:23.860
marry each other. The celibacy of that kind
was present in those days. And in that time

01:16:23.860 --> 01:16:29.410
when you were completely celibate, you were
innocent, you were given these Ashtang Yogas.

01:16:29.410 --> 01:16:36.410
There are eightfold paths [DEL: of Sahaj]
of this Hatha Yoga, out of which eighth one

01:16:37.730 --> 01:16:44.110
is Yama-niyama where the discipline and things
are there to maintain a proper life that was

01:16:44.110 --> 01:16:51.110
given to them. And then after that when that
was done, the maintenance of the proper life

01:16:51.870 --> 01:16:57.830
and all that was taught, also they were told
the exercises when according to the movement

01:16:57.830 --> 01:17:01.120
of the Kundalini wherever was the problem.

01:17:01.120 --> 01:17:07.410
Supposing the problem is in your particular
center, then you have to do that movement,

01:17:07.410 --> 01:17:12.540
that particular exercise you have to do. But
it’s, as I told you this morning, that your

01:17:12.540 --> 01:17:17.840
car has not started, you are still at home
and you are paying the toll for what? You

01:17:17.840 --> 01:17:23.780
must move, to find out where is the obstruction,
then you pay the toll. And nowadays it is

01:17:23.780 --> 01:17:29.760
so absurd that we take [DEL: the Saha–]
the Hatha Yoga in such a manner that we take

01:17:29.760 --> 01:17:36.170
the whole medicine box without having any
disease and get diseased. It’s a big science.

01:17:36.170 --> 01:17:41.580
Is a very big science one has to understand
that everything is correlated: How is your

01:17:41.580 --> 01:17:46.980
center, which center is catching, what center
requires what kind of treatment, how to clear

01:17:46.980 --> 01:17:49.160
it, and this technique you will learn in no
time. It’s very simple, once you get your

01:17:49.160 --> 01:17:49.410
realization.

01:17:49.250 --> 01:17:55.590
Question: Is there anything that we can start
doing now?

01:17:55.590 --> 01:18:01.490
Shri Mataji: Yes, just now I’m going to
give you realization. All right? That’s

01:18:01.490 --> 01:18:04.830
it, that’s just like a seeker, just like
a seeker.

01:18:04.830 --> 01:18:05.140
[Warren: On the sheet it tells them how to
meditate as well.

01:18:05.140 --> 01:18:05.390
Shri Mataji: Oh that I will tell later.]

01:18:05.340 --> 01:18:06.970
Ha. Now what about you? You have been raising
your hand.

01:18:06.970 --> 01:18:13.970
Question: What kind of a… what kind of a
yoga did Lord Krishna practice?

01:18:14.160 --> 01:18:20.060
Shri Mataji: Sahaj Yoga. [Shri Mataji chuckles.]

01:18:20.060 --> 01:18:26.380
Question: According to Yogananda, he said
that Lord Krishna practiced Kriya Yoga.

01:18:26.380 --> 01:18:29.520
Shri Mataji: Not at all, Is wrong. He, it
is just to apportion of himself to [INDISTINCT:

01:18:29.520 --> 01:18:36.520
you.] You see, Shri Krishna, if I have time
I can tell them, He in His Gita, He has prescribed

01:18:36.820 --> 01:18:43.820
four things. But Krishna was an incarnation
of diplomacy; He was an incarnation of divine

01:18:44.370 --> 01:18:51.370
diplomacy we should say, because when he told
Arjuna that you find it within yourself, the

01:18:53.650 --> 01:18:58.490
first thing, – He was not a businessman,
so He told the best thing first. He said,

01:18:58.490 --> 01:19:03.230
“Find it within yourself the gyana, the
awareness.” In your awareness you should

01:19:03.230 --> 01:19:09.500
find it, you should find your Spirit, should
become that. This is the first thing He told.

01:19:09.500 --> 01:19:16.500
But he was, that time a mediocre, an intellectual
I should say, and he said that “You are

01:19:16.700 --> 01:19:22.490
telling me to fight the war and here You are
saying that you find yourself and you become

01:19:22.490 --> 01:19:28.090
yourself, and to be a witness!” What Shri
Krishna meant was that you become a witness,

01:19:28.090 --> 01:19:32.600
then the whole thing becomes a drama, but
he didn’t understand.

01:19:32.600 --> 01:19:39.600
He, being a father, I give an analogy of a
father who is telling his son that, “The

01:19:40.490 --> 01:19:45.200
horse is behind the cart, so put the horse
in front so the cart will move.”

01:19:45.200 --> 01:19:49.930
But the son is saying that “Why not sitting
down here I move the cart?”

01:19:49.930 --> 01:19:54.750
So he says, “All right, go ahead.” He
says, “All right, go ahead,” because if

01:19:54.750 --> 01:19:59.960
you tell them straightforward they don’t
listen to you so tell them in another way.

01:19:59.960 --> 01:20:06.500
So the diplomacy, as the essence that you
give absurd conditions, such absurd conditions

01:20:06.500 --> 01:20:10.890
that people discover later on and find that
it was absurd.

01:20:10.890 --> 01:20:17.890
So the absurd condition He said that the first
thing you do is to do your karmas, do what

01:20:22.830 --> 01:20:26.960
you want to do and put it at the lotus feet
of the Lord – is an absurd condition. You

01:20:26.960 --> 01:20:33.880
cannot do it because your ego is intact, you
may believe, “I am serving the Lord.”

01:20:33.880 --> 01:20:39.030
You may believe it, “believe” is different
from reality, you are not. Because ego is

01:20:39.030 --> 01:20:44.500
there, and that’s why you feel hurt, sometimes
you take the credit. Unless and until you

01:20:44.500 --> 01:20:51.500
are realized, unless and until you become
a holy personality you’ll never say like

01:20:52.140 --> 01:20:56.500
that. After realization what do you say, “It’s
going, it’s coming, Mother it’s not working,

01:20:56.500 --> 01:20:59.840
it just doesn’t work.” “It,” you start
talking in a third person. You don’t say,

01:20:59.840 --> 01:21:06.840
“I’m giving you realization,” you don’t
say so. “It’s not working. It has worked.

01:21:07.940 --> 01:21:08.660
It has come up.”

01:21:08.660 --> 01:21:09.050
“What?”

01:21:09.050 --> 01:21:11.800
”Realization.” You don’t say “I.”

01:21:11.800 --> 01:21:17.190
So you become an akarmi, means like the sun
shines, it doesn’t say, “I shine.” There

01:21:17.190 --> 01:21:23.690
is no karma attached, this was the first thing
He said. But this absurdity people never saw,

01:21:23.690 --> 01:21:27.670
and they – even today people say, “I am
serving the Lord.” But you are not even

01:21:27.670 --> 01:21:34.670
connected, how are you serving Him? That’s
one thing. Because there is ego, you are identified

01:21:36.980 --> 01:21:41.760
with ego; actually you are serving your ego.
Unless and until you become realized, you

01:21:41.760 --> 01:21:47.680
do not serve God. This is one point which
was absurd, He told. Then second point – this

01:21:47.680 --> 01:21:48.840
is Karma Yoga.

01:21:48.840 --> 01:21:55.840
The second point He said was, that “You
should do Bhakti Yoga.” Bhakti Yoga is that

01:21:56.420 --> 01:22:02.980
you should worship Him, worship God, pray
to Him. But as usual because He was diplomacy

01:22:02.980 --> 01:22:08.430
He put a very interesting word called Ananya.
You should do Ananya Bhakti. Ananya means

01:22:08.430 --> 01:22:15.430
“when there is not the other.” When there
is not the other, when you are not the other,

01:22:17.200 --> 01:22:22.080
when you are one with God. That means all
those people who are talking, “Hare Rama,

01:22:22.080 --> 01:22:26.570
Hare Krishna, Hare Rama, Hare Krishna” on
Oxford Street are not connected. They are

01:22:26.570 --> 01:22:33.570
spoiling their throat, will get throat cancers.
You are not yet connected, you should be ananya.

01:22:34.070 --> 01:22:38.860
Ananya means you should be realized; you should
be connected with God.

01:22:38.860 --> 01:22:45.810
Imagine, supposing your President Reagan,
I go to him and stand before his house and

01:22:45.810 --> 01:22:49.980
start calling, “Reagan, Reagan, Reagan,”
I’ll be arrested. I must have a proper protocol,

01:22:49.980 --> 01:22:55.690
I must have proper permission, I should have
a proper way of going there, isn’t it?

01:22:55.690 --> 01:23:01.800
Everybody starts calling God as if He’s
in his pocket. “God give me a job, give

01:23:01.800 --> 01:23:08.800
me money, give me a car, give me this,”
I mean, imagine. You have to be connected

01:23:09.080 --> 01:23:13.460
with God. That’s what He said very clearly,
“ananya,” but these people, these are

01:23:13.460 --> 01:23:16.190
blind people they cannot see through.

01:23:16.190 --> 01:23:23.190
Then the third thing He said that, “It happens
within you that you get these happenings,”

01:23:25.110 --> 01:23:32.110
is the Kundalini Yoga. He said that when the
Kundalini starts, the jalandhara bhanda and

01:23:32.640 --> 01:23:38.780
all these bhandas take place when the Kundalini
rises. These granthis go into a particular

01:23:38.780 --> 01:23:43.640
kind of a formation like a car when you start
all the engines starts moving. So He described

01:23:43.640 --> 01:23:46.210
all the engine, how it moves.

01:23:46.210 --> 01:23:52.050
That, this Mr. Yogananda picked up and he
said He preached Kriya Yoga. That means if

01:23:52.050 --> 01:23:56.960
you, say, have a car which has stopped which
has not yet started, you move the wheel and

01:23:56.960 --> 01:24:03.960
you move all the machines, will it work? You
cannot do it. It happens automatically. It

01:24:07.110 --> 01:24:14.110
is spontaneous happening within us. When we
eat our food how the food is digested? Automatically.

01:24:16.000 --> 01:24:22.790
In the same way when Kundalini rises, to support
its rise all these bhandas and all these kriyas

01:24:22.790 --> 01:24:28.760
take place and kechari, also your tongue is
pulled in, so people they cut their tongues,

01:24:28.760 --> 01:24:35.650
put it back. Is that the way? Is absolutely
artificial, is stupid.

01:24:35.650 --> 01:24:42.570
To do like that, many people I have seen.
I don’t know the early ones who came, of

01:24:42.570 --> 01:24:47.870
Yogananda they had the tongues wagging like
that? Imagine by doing all these things, “take

01:24:47.870 --> 01:24:54.830
out your eyes, take out your nose.” This
is not the way. And that, “You suffer, you

01:24:54.830 --> 01:25:01.830
shave your heads, wear a kind of a cloth,”
you cannot. It’s a thing that’s living

01:25:04.820 --> 01:25:10.060
within you and acts in a living way. You cannot
just maneuver it artificially, you cannot.

01:25:10.060 --> 01:25:14.980
It has to start!. Like even this camera, you
see, a television, anything, this has to be

01:25:14.980 --> 01:25:21.360
put to the mains. You cannot start with your
finger the camera working, can you? The electricity

01:25:21.360 --> 01:25:28.360
has to be there, in the same way energy of
Kundalini has to be there to work it out.

01:25:30.970 --> 01:25:34.560
This is absurd.

01:25:34.560 --> 01:25:41.560
So the Kriya Yoga, which is described by Shri
Krishna, is the living process. He said, “Is

01:25:42.750 --> 01:25:49.120
the living tree.” I’m surprised. We can…
human beings are very great, I must say, the

01:25:49.120 --> 01:25:56.120
way they make a pai out of everyone. So all
these great incarnations came on this earth;

01:25:58.040 --> 01:26:05.040
they wrote it very clearly; they said everything
very clearly; it was very simple; there was

01:26:05.390 --> 01:26:11.990
nothing to be so much deluded – of course
he used a word like ananya. You see in any

01:26:11.990 --> 01:26:18.990
dictionary what is the meaning of word ananya
is, mean is “when is there is not the other.”

01:26:22.540 --> 01:26:26.590
What have we made of Christ, what have we
made of Krishna, what have we made of Rama?

01:26:26.590 --> 01:26:33.150
When I see this I’m amazed. But you can’t
make anything out of Me, because you will

01:26:33.150 --> 01:26:40.150
get your realization. After that, if you try
to do anything to Me, you lose your vibrations,

01:26:41.770 --> 01:26:42.560
straightforward.

01:26:42.560 --> 01:26:44.500
I can tell you this much.

01:26:44.500 --> 01:26:51.500
There was a gentleman who got his realization
from Me, an Indian. Typically he went to New

01:26:51.830 --> 01:26:58.700
York, started his thing and then in Los Angeles
he started a Sahaj Yoga center, and he came

01:26:58.700 --> 01:27:05.530
back to see Me in Bombay, and the Sahaj Yogis
told that “He is just giving us a fit. Is

01:27:05.530 --> 01:27:09.830
horrible. His vibrations are horrible.”

01:27:09.830 --> 01:27:11.000
I said, “I know that, you don’t talk to
him.”

01:27:11.000 --> 01:27:14.730
So I called him, I said, “What do you do?”

01:27:14.730 --> 01:27:21.730
“Oh, I have started a big thing there in
Los Angeles and in New York and this and that.”

01:27:21.740 --> 01:27:28.060
“All right, can I have a brochure?” You
won’t believe he had written, that for ordinary

01:27:28.060 --> 01:27:35.060
vibrations seventy-five dollars and for extraordinary,
special vibrations hundred and seventy-five

01:27:35.820 --> 01:27:36.320
dollars.

01:27:36.320 --> 01:27:41.510
So I said, “Oh God, what’s this?” I
said, “How do you do this way?”

01:27:41.510 --> 01:27:45.080
He says, “Yes Mother, that’s [DEL: what]
how we are to do. After all, I have to live.”

01:27:45.080 --> 01:27:49.810
I said, “You have to live, all right, you
do your work that you were doing. You were

01:27:49.810 --> 01:27:53.900
teaching something, you do that, but you cannot
sell these vibrations; I didn’t give you

01:27:53.900 --> 01:28:00.900
for selling. Did you buy from Me?” And he
wouldn’t believe. And he was very angry

01:28:02.980 --> 01:28:04.490
and then he went away.

01:28:04.490 --> 01:28:08.820
He said, “There’s a guru who is in Calicut,
He’s a very wonderful man.”

01:28:08.820 --> 01:28:10.500
I said, “You go and see him.”

01:28:10.500 --> 01:28:14.470
He went and saw him, and this guru wouldn’t
allow him to enter into his house. He threw

01:28:14.470 --> 01:28:19.400
stones at him. He wouldn’t allow him to
enter even the gate. So he went back to the

01:28:19.400 --> 01:28:25.820
station, so he was sitting down there, then
somebody met him from the guru, he said that

01:28:25.820 --> 01:28:32.090
“Guru was saying that, ‘he went and insulted
Mother and how does he come to be here? I’ll

01:28:32.090 --> 01:28:37.290
not see his face.’” Then he sat there
for three days, and he was allowed to go,

01:28:37.290 --> 01:28:43.600
and then guru sent a very good poem about
Me in Sanskrit language, which he read it

01:28:43.600 --> 01:28:44.570
out to Me.

01:28:44.570 --> 01:28:51.570
But the fellow is just the same still. He’s
not changed; he’s just the same. Now he

01:28:53.540 --> 01:28:57.090
has no vibrations, he’s not a Sahaj yogi,
he has nothing to do, but he has an ashram,

01:28:57.090 --> 01:29:00.250
he’s making money out of it. Of course we
have withdrawn our photographs and everything

01:29:00.250 --> 01:29:06.080
but he’s just the same, what am I to do?
He is now making them stand on their heads

01:29:06.080 --> 01:29:12.540
and do all kinds of things. And he has more
people than you are here. That’s the best

01:29:12.540 --> 01:29:19.540
part of it. People are more attracted to these
things than to reality. Is very true.

01:29:20.770 --> 01:29:27.340
When I came last time to America there was
a lady. I told her that, “Your guru was

01:29:27.340 --> 01:29:29.720
believing in all miracles, and you better
not start it.”

01:29:29.720 --> 01:29:34.280
She said, “No, no, no, no. I want the ultimate,
I want the parama, I’m not going to go into

01:29:34.280 --> 01:29:34.640
it.”

01:29:34.640 --> 01:29:36.850
I said, “All right. Promise Me.”

01:29:36.850 --> 01:29:40.970
She said, “Yes.” But then she started
getting some sort of a rice falling from her

01:29:40.970 --> 01:29:47.190
hand and all that and then she started doing
her things, you see? She called people told

01:29:47.190 --> 01:29:52.260
them even the name of the horses which are
going to win, all sorts of things. And you

01:29:52.260 --> 01:29:59.260
won’t believe, when I went back to America
to My most embarrassed condition, I found

01:30:00.360 --> 01:30:07.360
that she had three thousand disciples falling
at her feet. And she was absolutely possessed.

01:30:09.910 --> 01:30:11.680
She came to Me and I told her, “What are
you doing?”

01:30:11.680 --> 01:30:13.770
She said, “Mother, this is the powers You
have given me.”

01:30:13.770 --> 01:30:17.780
I said, “I have never given you these powers
to beat people and tell them about horses.

01:30:17.780 --> 01:30:19.060
Is absurd.”

01:30:19.060 --> 01:30:23.360
She said, “But this is happening to me.”

01:30:23.360 --> 01:30:29.810
I said, “All supraconscious, all nonsense.”
She wouldn’t listen. I said, “All right,

01:30:29.810 --> 01:30:32.450
tell this gentleman about his future.”

01:30:32.450 --> 01:30:37.390
She told him something. He said , “It’s
all wrong, it’s not true.”

01:30:37.390 --> 01:30:40.810
I said, “Tell this lady.” She couldn’t
tell.

01:30:40.810 --> 01:30:45.090
So she said, “Mother, have you taken away
my powers?”

01:30:45.090 --> 01:30:47.420
I said, “If they were your powers, I would
have garlanded, I would have worshiped you,

01:30:47.420 --> 01:30:52.260
but they are not yours, they have gone, finished.”
But she would not give up, you see popularity,

01:30:52.260 --> 01:30:58.400
she was on with it. Now only thing is she’s
in a lunatic asylum.

01:30:58.400 --> 01:31:05.400
So all these things they do, they know how
to make these things, they are so superficial.

01:31:10.180 --> 01:31:14.670
They don’t know what injuries they are doing
to themselves and to others.

01:31:14.670 --> 01:31:19.990
Now, who were asking some question?

01:31:19.990 --> 01:31:26.990
Man. I wanted to ask You about the meditations
from the Maharishi Mahayoga, what Your opinion

01:31:30.000 --> 01:31:30.550
was.

01:31:30.550 --> 01:31:36.930
Shri Mataji: Now again the controversy, again
the controversy, the less said the better.

01:31:36.930 --> 01:31:39.000
All right?

01:31:39.000 --> 01:31:40.090
Man: The what?

01:31:40.090 --> 01:31:47.090
Shri Mataji: The less said the better. For
example, the mantras he gives you. You know

01:31:48.740 --> 01:31:53.790
what they mean, one of them, inga ? It means
“the tail of the scorpion.” Now where

01:31:53.790 --> 01:32:00.270
is the scorpion and where is the tail? When
the Kundalini has started, then you should

01:32:00.270 --> 01:32:06.050
know which center it is catching and what
mantra to be said. It is not that you can

01:32:06.050 --> 01:32:13.050
just give a mantra and charge three hundred
pounds, and people do pay. And this flying

01:32:13.050 --> 01:32:17.400
squad that he has started, the head of that
flying squad here he is, is sitting down here,

01:32:17.400 --> 01:32:22.550
he will tell you. The head of that where he
went and learnt from him flying, so called,

01:32:22.550 --> 01:32:26.230
he suffered from epilepsy, his wife suffered
from epilepsy, his daughter suffered from

01:32:26.230 --> 01:32:33.230
epilepsy, and they came to Me and they wrote
to him about Me, in that miserable condition.

01:32:34.450 --> 01:32:38.690
He was the head; he was going to teach them
flying.

01:32:38.690 --> 01:32:43.280
I told him, “Why don’t you ask your guru
to go on this leaning tower of Pisa and make

01:32:43.280 --> 01:32:50.280
him fly? And you pay him some money for that,
will be good idea.” They paid three thousand

01:32:51.520 --> 01:32:58.520
pounds for flying. You are not going to become
birds now, are you?

01:33:00.790 --> 01:33:05.630
But it is very difficult, you know, to accept
really because you have paid so much money.

01:33:05.630 --> 01:33:11.410
This is like, “We have paid it, so better
have it.” You see whatever… Like you go

01:33:11.410 --> 01:33:18.410
to a restaurant and you pay for it, and may
be bad but you eat it. You see, after all,

01:33:18.880 --> 01:33:20.550
you have paid for it.

01:33:20.550 --> 01:33:24.780
That’s human nature, isn’t it? Oh, it’s
terrible. It’s terrible, and difficult to

01:33:24.780 --> 01:33:29.210
give realization to people from all these
gurus, I can tell you, Yogananda… or this,

01:33:29.210 --> 01:33:32.450
what’s his name is? This Bhandasura’s
name, what is his name?

01:33:32.450 --> 01:33:33.040
Warren: Muktananda.

01:33:33.040 --> 01:33:40.040
Shri Mataji: Muktananda. I know them very
well, I know them. I’ve known them for ages,

01:33:40.920 --> 01:33:44.880
and they know Me too.

01:33:44.880 --> 01:33:47.600
Yes?

01:33:47.600 --> 01:33:54.600
Lady: Are there other sources where you can
reach your realization other than through

01:33:58.920 --> 01:33:59.170
You?

01:33:59.160 --> 01:34:00.130
[Warren repeats the question.]

01:34:00.130 --> 01:34:04.020
Shri Mataji: Through Me? It’s not a question
of through Me or anything; it’s through

01:34:04.020 --> 01:34:06.310
your Kundalini, is your Kundalini within you.

01:34:06.310 --> 01:34:08.880
Lady: Is there someone else that can guide
you or…?

01:34:08.880 --> 01:34:13.530
Shri Mataji: I don’t know, I haven’t seen
many. I wish somebody could, like – you

01:34:13.530 --> 01:34:18.990
see people are very much hurt to see that
I’m doing it. I said, “Baba, you do it.

01:34:18.990 --> 01:34:21.090
I’ll be very happy to retire, really.”

01:34:21.090 --> 01:34:22.610
They said, “Why You, Mother?”

01:34:22.610 --> 01:34:27.710
I said, “Really, I don’t know why I was
chosen for this. It’s a thankless job. You

01:34:27.710 --> 01:34:34.710
must have tremendous patience, I tell you.
The day I retire my husband will pay you for

01:34:36.570 --> 01:34:39.630
that. I can assure you.”

01:34:39.630 --> 01:34:46.630
He’s telling Me that “You are trying to
put patches to the heavens which are falling.”

01:34:47.790 --> 01:34:54.790
He doesn’t believe that I can do it. Is
a thankless job, absolutely a thankless job.

01:34:55.420 --> 01:34:58.950
But what to do?

01:34:58.950 --> 01:35:05.950
Once I did feel little frustrated, and I said,
“Let it be now. Doesn’t matter, let the

01:35:06.930 --> 01:35:13.460
destruction come in.” And then you know
this clever man, he brought a photograph of

01:35:13.460 --> 01:35:18.820
Mine, with My eyes so compassionate, such
compassion flowing, I said, “Better do it.

01:35:18.820 --> 01:35:25.090
It’s You, what can You do? You can’t get
out of it, that’s what You are.”

01:35:25.090 --> 01:35:31.220
So I have to do it, My children, I have to
do it. If you could do it, I’ll be very

01:35:31.220 --> 01:35:36.570
happy. Any one, I’ll be extremely happy
and retire.

01:35:36.570 --> 01:35:42.290
Warren softly: Other Sahaja Yogis can.

01:35:42.290 --> 01:35:49.290
Shri Mataji: Ha, Of course! Other Sahaj yogis
can give you realization. For example Warren

01:35:49.500 --> 01:35:55.090
himself has given realization to I don’t
know how many thousand. But I know of a person

01:35:55.090 --> 01:36:01.450
who has given realization to more than ten
thousand people, in India. Yes! Yes, yes,

01:36:01.450 --> 01:36:05.710
you can give realization, you can give it,
all right?

01:36:05.710 --> 01:36:12.330
Man: Is the lotus position any special advantage
over sitting normally?

01:36:12.330 --> 01:36:15.550
Warren: Is the lotus position any special
advantage?

01:36:15.550 --> 01:36:21.850
Shri Mataji: Not in Sahaj Yoga, not in Sahaj
Yoga. You see now God has decided to give

01:36:21.850 --> 01:36:27.920
you in any position you sit; He has to save
His creation. Many people can’t even sit

01:36:27.920 --> 01:36:33.370
on the ground, so they are not to be forced
now. Whatever position you have, you are all

01:36:33.370 --> 01:36:40.230
right. You drink, all right. You take drugs,
all right. You are a thief, all right. Any

01:36:40.230 --> 01:36:47.230
kind, come along. Once you get realization
these things will drop out. This is the trick.

01:36:48.380 --> 01:36:55.380
Better come along and have it. There’s no
position required, nothing required, only

01:37:14.750 --> 01:37:21.750
the desire to
be the Spirit, that’s all.

01:37:56.560 --> 01:38:03.560
First one man: We’ll take it.

01:38:15.570 --> 01:38:22.570
[several people start to echo the request:
“We’ll take it.”]

01:38:32.640 --> 01:38:35.460
Warren: They want it.

01:38:35.460 --> 01:38:39.540
Shri Mataji: Now they want it, that’s all.

01:38:39.540 --> 01:38:43.020
Man: May we have it.

01:38:43.020 --> 01:38:50.020
Shri Mataji: So, that’s all, that’s the
best way. All right?

01:39:41.670 --> 01:39:48.670
Now those who got

01:40:40.240 --> 01:40:47.240
it yesterday are here, some of them, and those
who have come for

01:43:22.860 --> 01:43:29.860
the first time are also here.

01:44:36.190 --> 01:44:43.190
Two ladies: what’s wrong with that? What
was that again?

01:45:07.550 --> 01:45:14.550
Warren: They just want
You
to repeat that, “those that have..”

01:46:37.270 --> 01:46:44.270
Shri Mataji: No, yesterday some people got
realization and

01:49:56.420 --> 01:50:03.420
some of

01:51:06.380 --> 01:51:13.380
you are new people. We’ll have to, later
on, see them, those who are new. And those

01:51:41.280 --> 01:51:48.280
who got realization, specially yesterday,
I
would like to meet them. As yesterday I couldn’t

01:51:59.950 --> 01:52:06.950
meet them. So I would like to meet them and
those who are new, also we’ll if we can

01:52:57.990 --> 01:53:04.990
work it out…

